DOCUMENT();

loadMacros(
"PG.pl",
"PGbasicmacros.pl",
"PGchoicemacros.pl",
"PGanswermacros.pl",
"PGauxiliaryFunctions.pl"
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(2,6,1);
$b = random(2,9,1);
$d = random(4,10,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));

Evaluate the integral by interpreting it in terms of areas:
$BR
$PAR
\( \displaystyle{ \int_{0}^{$d}  |$b x - $a| \, dx} = \)
$PAR
   \{ans_rule(25) \}
$BR
$BR

EOT

$ans = $a**2/(2*$b) + ($d - $a/$b)*($b*$d - $a)/2;

ANS(num_cmp($ans));

ENDDOCUMENT();
